<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278792>
    dc:description "PLATE 120. A–C, E. Chelae, holotypes. D. Scutum and metathorax + propodeum, holotype. A. Gonatopus asiae (=Apterodryinus asiaticus) (from Olmi 1984). B. G. hagoromo. C. G. insulae (=Apterodryinus insularis) (from Olmi 1984). D. G. lini (courtesy of Michael Sharkey). Length 1.15 mm. E. G. lini (from Olmi 1995a). Scale bar 0.29 mm for A, 0.22 mm for B, 0.12 mm for C and 0.19 mm for E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

